<Vertical id="fba2_abc_reference" when="!@fba2_completion_checkbox.value">
<Markdown id="fba2_abc_reference_intro">
## ABC Reference Diagrams

Each diagram shows the **Antecedent → Behavior → Consequence** chain for one function of behavior.
</Markdown>

<Markdown id="fba2_abc_ref_escape_label">### Escape (Negative Reinforcement)</Markdown>
<Mermaid id="fba2_abc_ref_escape" src="diagrams/abc_ref_escape.mmd" />

<Markdown id="fba2_abc_ref_attention_label">### Attention (Positive Reinforcement)</Markdown>
<Mermaid id="fba2_abc_ref_attention" src="diagrams/abc_ref_attention.mmd" />

