<HH> ============= Screen: Textbook on escape =================== </HH>

<Markdown id="fba2_textbook_escape" when="!@fba2_completion_checkbox.value">
**Brainstorm**: _Consider as many strategies and interventions as possible. Defer clinical judgment._
- Prevent the problem behavior from occurring using antecedent event and predictor strategies.
- Teach adaptive behaviors that lead to the same outcome as the problem behavior using teaching strategies.
- React to the problem behavior in an appropriate way by using consequence strategies.
- React to desired behaviors by making reinforcement at a higher rate, more immediate, and of higher quality by using consequence strategies.
- Make desired behaviors take less effort to perform to obtain the same consequence.
</Markdown>

    <!-- Textbook information on designing interventions -->
<Markdown id="fba2_textbook_interventions" when="!@fba2_completion_checkbox.value">
## Generate interventions based on the competing behavior model
**Brainstorm**: _Consider as many strategies and interventions as possible. Defer clinical judgment._

- Prevent the problem behavior from occurring using antecedent event and predictor strategies.
- Teach adaptive behaviors that lead to the same outcome as the problem behavior using teaching strategies.
- React to the problem behavior in an appropriate way by using consequence strategies.
- React to desired behaviors by making reinforcement at a higher rate, more immediate, and of higher quality by using consequence strategies.
- Make desired behaviors take less effort to perform to obtain the same consequence.
</Markdown>


