<Vertical id="fba2_email_revised_plan_tab" title="Your revised plan">
<Use ref="fba2_revised_plan" />
</Vertical>
<Vertical id="fba2_email_escape_plan_tab" title="The escape plan">
<Use ref="fba2_plan_reference" />
</Vertical>
<Vertical id="fba2_email_likes_tab" title="What you like about the escape plan">
<Use ref="fba2_plan_likes" />
</Vertical>
<Vertical id="fba2_email_sensory_plan_tab" title="The sensory plan">
<Use ref="fba2_sensory_plan_reference" />
</Vertical>
</Tabs>
</Vertical>

<Vertical id="fba2_final_email_completed"  when="@fba2_completion_checkbox.value">
  <Use ref="fba2_final_email_entry" />
</Vertical>

<HH> ============= Screen: Completion ========================== </HH>

<Vertical id="fba2_completion_page">
<Markdown id="fba2_completion_confirm_label">**Confirm that you are done with this exercise.**</Markdown>

<CheckboxInput id="fba2_completion_checkbox">
<Key id="fba2_part_3auto_finished">I don't need to make any more changes</Key>
</CheckboxInput>

<IntakeGate id="fba2_completion_gate" ready="id('fba2_part_3auto_finished') in @fba2_completion_checkbox.value">
<Markdown id="fba2_completion_spacer"> </Markdown>
<Markdown id="fba2_completion_summary">
- In this activity, you learned about the **function of behavior** (attention, escape,
  access/tangibles, sensory), the **ABCs** (Antecedent, Behavior, Consequence), and
  **Competing Behavior Pathways**. You used these concepts to develop an **intervention
  plan** for Johnny's bedtime escape behavior.
- Next time, you will follow up on the intervention plan and learn about **progress
  monitoring** and **implementation fidelity**.

## PLEASE CLICK CONTINUE TO REVIEW YOUR RESPONSES AND SAVE THEM TO A PDF. THEN UPLOAD THE PDF TO YOUR COURSE SYSTEM.
</Markdown>
</IntakeGate>
</Vertical>

